---
<footer class="footer" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr auto; background:var(--teal);">
  <div style="padding:22px 24px; border-right:2px solid rgba(232,224,204,0.18);">
    <div style="font-size:22px; font-weight:500; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--cream); line-height:1.05;">
      Let's build<br>something.
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(232,224,204,0.45); margin-top:5px;">
      fercitotron@gmail.com · github.com/FernandoJRR
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ft-btns" style="display:flex; flex-direction:row; align-items:stretch;">
    <a
      href="https://github.com/FernandoJRR"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      style="display:flex; align-items:center; padding:0 18px; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.25); color:rgba(232,224,204,0.65); border-right:2px solid rgba(232,224,204,0.15); transition:background 120ms, color 120ms;"
      onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(0,0,0,0.4)'; this.style.color='var(--cream)'"
      onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(0,0,0,0.25)'; this.style.color='rgba(232,224,204,0.65)'"
    >GitHub</a>
    <a
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/fernando-rodríguez-0a68a827b"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      style="display:flex; align-items:center; padding:0 18px; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.25); color:rgba(232,224,204,0.65); border-right:2px solid rgba(232,224,204,0.15); transition:background 120ms, color 120ms;"
      onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(0,0,0,0.4)'; this.style.color='var(--cream)'"
      onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(0,0,0,0.25)'; this.style.color='rgba(232,224,204,0.65)'"
    >LinkedIn</a>
    <a
      href="mailto:fercitotron@gmail.com"
      style="display:flex; align-items:center; padding:0 18px; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; background:var(--amber); color:var(--bg); transition:background 120ms;"
      onmouseover="this.style.background='#b8791f'"
      onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--amber)'"
    >Get in touch →</a>
  </div>
</footer>
